  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595969409045-A5LZJZJGTLRSDTXQZ06K/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Back in the studio after being away for quite some time. As much as I enjoy traveling and being on the road, there's nothing quite like coming home. Loved reading all the comments and quote suggestions in <a href=\"https://youtu.be/zVRQTrABBs4\">this video</a>. Decided to script my favorite one that I am feeling in a major way today, so thanks Amy Fentress for bringing it up! For me this week is all about getting back into the groove. Putting my focus and energy on projects that I am really excited about showing you soon! What are you up to this week?</p><p>I'm using <a href=\"http://goo.gl/zMVzgS\">this watercolor set from Michaels</a> and a waterbrush <a href=\"http://goo.gl/eDsF0u\">that I love by Tim Holtz/Ranger</a>. If you have a favorite quote – silly, snarky or simple in its’ wisdom, please share in the comments!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
